title: Women in Power: Press for Progress - Lift as You Rise
description:
In recognition of International Women's Day, a panel discussion highlighting women in leadership roles throughout the City, including a keynote address by Mayor Jenny Durkan.

Speakers and panelists:
Sarah Davis, Chair of WIP (Seattle City Light)
Jenny A. Durkan, Mayor of Seattle
Shefali Ranganathan, Deputy Mayor
Carmen Best, Interim Chief of Police
Tracye Cantrell, Acting Director, Seattle IT
Moderator: Michelle Vargo, Director of Network, Substations and Service Operations (Seattle City Light)
